c: 59
v: 2
t: "Yena uyilowo owakhipha labo abangakholwanga phakathi kwabantu bencwadi ezindlini zabo (emizini yabo) ekuhlanganeni kokuqala anicabanganga ukuthi bayophuma futhi babecabanga ukuthi izinqaba zezindlu zabo ziyobavikela kuMvelinqangi, manjalo uMvelinqangi weza kubona evela lapho babengalindele khona futhi wafaka uvalo ezinhliziyweni zabo bebhidliza izindlu zabo ngezandla zabo kanye nezandla zabakholwayo ngakho-ke yalekani Oh Bantu abanamehlo"